zozo:
d1 $ every 2 (rev) (s "~ [z-sn:6*2] z-sn:6 ~") # gain 0.8
d2 $ n "1 ~ 3*2 4" # s "bubble" # sustain "0.3 0.02 0.02 0.02" # gain 1.2
d3 $ s "z-hh:3 ~ z-hh:3*2 ~" # pan (range 0.25 0.75 $ rand) # gain 0.8

d1 $ every 2 (|- crush "1") $ every 2 (rev) (s "bd*2 ~ z-sn:3 z-sn:3") # crush "3"
d2 $ n "[-2 .. -3]" # s "rave2"
d1 $ every 4 (const $ n "3 1*8 4 2" # sound "bend" # crush "10") $ n "1 1*10 1 1" # sound "bend" # crush "5"
d1 $ whenmod 4 2 (rev) $ s "bend*2 east:2 east*4 east:2*2" # pan sine # sustain tri

d1 $ stack [
n "9 4 9 ~ 3 6" # sustain 1 # sound "supermandolin" # cutoff (range 300 520 $ slow 4 $ sine) # crush "3.5" # gain 1.4,
n "-6" # sound "superchip" # cutoff (range 300 800 $ slow 4 $tri) # crush "2" # gain 0.8,
n "1 3 6~ 8 3" #sustain 0.3 # sound "superpiano" # crush "5" # gain 0.6
]
d1 $ every 2 (|- crush 2) $ n (irand 10) # s "super808" # crush 5 # sustain "1 0.3" # pan "-0.8 -0.4 0.2 0.4 -0.2 0.8"
d1 $ stack [every 2 (stut 2 0.7 0.5) $ stut 4 0.3 0.2 $ n "1 2 4 6*2" # sound "h", sound "bd [~bd] bd*2 bd"]
d1 $ stack [n "4*128" # s "control" # cutoff (range 400 800 $ slow 4 $ tri) # crush (run 4) # sustain "0.2 0.3 0.5 0.6 0.8", rot "<0 2 0 2>" $ stut 2 0.2 0.3 $ s "z-kik:4*3 techno:4*2"]
dave:
d1 $ every 4 (fast 0.75) $ note "[-12 ~ 12 7]*4" # n "0 1 2 3" # sound "clubkick"
d2 $ every 4 (fast 2) $ note "[-24 ~ 12 7]*4" # n "0 1 2 3" # sound "industrial"
d1 $ every 2 (fast 1.25) $ slow 0.5 $ note "-3 12 0 ~ ~ 27" # n "1" # sound "sid"
d1 $ palindrome $ every 3 (fast 2) $ iter 8 $ note "9 7? -5? -12? 30 40 -22 40 ~ 10 50 -12? ~"  # sound "909" #lpf 1200
d1 $ note "0 [0 ~ 12? 0 ~ 1? 0]" # n (irand 4) # s "stab" # pan rand # gain rand
d1 $ sound "bd*1024" # n (irand 8) # speed (fast 1200 $ range 0.5 1 tri) # lpf 4000 #lpq rand #djf sine
